# This React Native app installs STANDALONE (not as a pnpm workspace member).
# A flat, app-local node_modules is required because:
#   - RN's Gradle files resolve native modules via app-relative ../node_modules paths
#   - Metro resolves from the app's node_modules
#   - Reanimated 4 + react-native-worklets MUST be a single physical copy; pnpm's
#     symlinked/peer-isolated layout otherwise produces two worklets copies and the
#     app crashes (SIGABRT in libworklets) the moment a worklet runs.
# Install with:  pnpm install --ignore-workspace   (run inside apps/user-app-v2)
node-linker=hoisted
